https://github.com/alankrantas/svelteapp-typescript-go



Download Dependencies
# download frontend dependencies
yarn

# download backend dependencies
yarn setup-server

# download both dependencies
yarn setup-full
# or
# yarn setup-all
Upgrade Dependencies
# upgrade frontend dependencies
yarn upgrade-app

# upgrade backend dependencies
yarn upgrade-server

# upgrade both dependencies
yarn upgrade-full
# or
# yarn upgrade-all
Build Production
Install dependencies, build both front-end and back-end apps and run the local server:

# build frontend app
yarn build-app

# build backend server (which will set CGO_ENABLED=1)
yarn build-server

# build both
yarn build-full
# or
# yarn build
# yarn build-all


# start backend
./main

# start frontend
yarn run serve



# 以下の方法はapiリクエスト受けれない

./_start_lighttpd.sh

open 3000




